    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Ecology",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> temperate plains<br/><b>Organization</b> solitary, pair, or herd (3\u201330)<br/><b>Treasure</b> none"
        },
        {
            "name": "Special Abilities",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Stampede (Ex)</b> A stampede occurs if three or more creatures with stampede make a trample attack while remaining adjacent to each other. While stampeding, the creatures can trample foes of their size or smaller, and the trample\u2019s save DC increases by +2."
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Aurochs (both singular and plural) are large herd animals similar to domesticated cattle."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>This large, horned bull has a dirty black hide and an aggressive temper. Its horns are wide and sharp.</i>",
